## 🏗️ 상태 머신 패턴들

### 패턴 1: 단순 상태

```rust
enum State {
    Running,
    Stopped,
}

match state {
    State::Running => println!("실행 중"),
    State::Stopped => println!("정지됨"),
}
```

### 패턴 2: 데이터를 가진 상태

```rust
enum State {
    Running(u8),    // 출력값
    Error(String),  // 에러 메시지
}

match state {
    State::Running(power) => println!("Power: {}", power),
    State::Error(msg) => println!("Error: {}", msg),
}
```

### 패턴 3: 복잡한 상태 데이터

```rust
struct PowerInfo {
    current: u8,
    max: u8,
}

enum State {
    Running(PowerInfo),
    Error { message: String, code: u32 },
}
```

### 패턴 4: 상태 전이 함수

```rust
fn transition(current: State, command: &str) -> State {
    match (current, command) {
        (State::Idle, "START") => State::Running(10),
        (State::Running(p), "POWER_UP") => State::Running(p + 20),
        (_, _) => current, // 유효하지 않은 전이는 상태 유지
    }
}
```

### 패턴 5: 상태별 행동

```rust
fn execute(state: &State) {
    match state {
        State::Idle => println!("대기 중..."),
        State::Running(power) => println!("Power: {}", power),
        State::Error(msg) => println!("Error: {}", msg),
    }
}
```

